title: Rugby World Cup 2015: Fresh Wales worry over Roberts and Williams
text: Liam Williams and Jamie Roberts have given Wales fresh World Cup scares after coming off during their Pool A defeat by Australia at Twickenham. Scarlets wing wing Williams and Harlequins centre Roberts departed in the dying stages. More to follow. Also related to this story Share this story Share this page
